<p itemprop="description">A test engineer designs, develops, and maintains automated testing solutions and infrastructure. They create comprehensive test automation frameworks, implement continuous testing practices, and ensure robust quality assurance through engineering excellence.</p>

<section class="role-details">
    <h2>Typical responsibilities</h2>
    <ul>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Design and develop automated test frameworks and testing infrastructure</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Create and maintain comprehensive automated test suites</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Implement continuous integration and continuous testing practices</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Collaborate with development teams on testable software design</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Perform performance, security, and accessibility testing</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Monitor and maintain test environments and testing tools</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Provide technical guidance on testing approaches and strategies</li>
    </ul>
</section>

